# Testing : DMA: Suspend and Resume (OFF mode)
# Results : Target: OFF mode / Device OFF
#           DMA driver shall use clocks, power domain, voltage domain on a need
#           basis and relinquish when not needed, via the respective manager.
#           Drivers shall check if context restore is needed when driver is activated
